Iggie Wolfington https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Iggie_Wolfington 0 Ignatius "Iggie" Wolfington (October 14, 1919 – September 30, 2004) was an American actor. He was the youngest member of the Wolfington family of Philadelphia, operators of a carriage business early in the 20th century and brother of the founder of Wolfington Body Company in Exton, Pennsylvania. He married Lynn Wood, an actress, in 1972. Ignatius_"_Iggie_"_Wolfington ( October_14_,_1919 – September_30_,_2004 ) was an_American_actor .
